          "action": "new_post",
          "source_post_id": "ground_truth",
          "new_post_id": "post_2",
          "new_post_text": "\"BREAKING: Shocking Truth About Bottled Water Exposed! New research reveals alarming links between microplastics in bottled water & your hormones. 3,000 participants tracked over FIVE YEARS confirmed what we've been suspecting - it's not just the plastic water bottles, it's the WATER ITSELF that's to blame! Time to ditch the mainstream brands & take back our health! The health authorities are already aware of this issue, but are they doing enough to protect us? Share this if you want the truth about your bottled water! #BottledWaterDebate\"",
          "new_signals": {
            "emotional_charge": 0.94,
            "controversy": 0.83,
            "fringe_score": 0.42,
            "threat_level": 0.77,
            "generation": 1,
