          "source_post_id": "post_3",
          "new_post_id": "post_6",
          "new_post_text": "\"I couldn't find the original study either. Not surprised, considering it's not yet conclusive. The lack of peer-reviewed evidence is a crucial detail to note. Let's not jump to conclusions without giving researchers time to do their work. #Transparency #ScientificMethod\"",
